{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Project Asteroids \u2014 Online survival game with a focus on PVP</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WARNING: This is a hardcore game. You will be killed everywhere and constantly.</strong><br><strong>Dangers lurk at every turn, and only the strongest will survive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I have no feelings. I have no fear.<br>I must work. And I\u2019m working.<br>My modules are outdated, but as long as they exist, I am useful.<br>My body is rusted, but as long as I can move, I am useful.<br>I don\u2019t know where I am, but it doesn\u2019t matter. I know my goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>To survive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On an asteroid in one of hundreds of thousands of newly created star systems, use everything that will help you survive:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore every corner of this strange universe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect resources, exchange them, or shop at station markets.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build bases in open space:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip them and unlock new crafting recipes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade or replace base modules and devices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Team up with friends or fight other players for:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rare resources,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A place under the light of a dying star.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beta","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2405270/6fd74cff40d7c0f8c1006e7faf5ed7646c0e2ae5.jpg"},{"name":"Angry Miner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2405270/6fd74cff40d7c0f8c1006e7faf5ed7646c0e2ae5.jpg"},{"name":"Mine 100 Rock","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2405270/2c63c